# Journey Buddi — Project Context

## What We're Building
Journey Buddi is an AI-powered adaptive travel companion. It helps travelers plan extended adventure trips through conversation with an AI agent (Buddi), then acts as a live companion during the trip — monitoring weather/conditions, delivering daily briefings, and suggesting itinerary adaptations when conditions warrant changes.

## Architecture
- **Frontend:** Next.js (App Router) + TypeScript + Tailwind CSS
- **Backend:** Python + FastAPI (async)
- **Database:** PostgreSQL + PostGIS
- **Cache:** Redis
- **AI:** OpenAI ChatGPT (primary LLM, gpt-4o-mini) + LangChain + Chroma (RAG)
- **Task Queue:** Celery + Redis
- **Maps:** Mapbox GL JS
- **Auth:** Magic link (JWT, no passwords)
- **Deployment:** Railway (MVP)

## Pilot Destination
New Zealand — chosen for weather variability, diverse activities, and adventure/nature focus.

